Description_lang: The trolls of the desert who worshipped Sethraliss used these blowguns to hunt their prey, be it beast, or troll. The poison the darts were dipped in would paralyze their prey, and within a minute, kill them. "The Prick of Sethraliss" was whispered to children in order to keep them in line, as was written in an ancient poem: "Should the young turn defiant, show anger or malice, the winds of Vol'Dun will bring the Prick of Sethraliss."
